                  on the earth because of the availability of water. Itself
                  being tasteless, odorless and colorless, it adds taste,
                  color and nice smell in the life of living beings on the
                  earth. It is found everywhere and known as life. It takes
                  nothing from us but gives life to us. It has no shape but
                  takes the shape of container we store it. We find it
                  everywhere in rivers, seas, tanks, wells, ponds, etc but we
                  lack clean drinking water. Three-fourth part of the earth is
                  full of water however we need to conserve water as there is
                  very less percentage of clean water.
